'''高齡產婦'''較廣義的定義是指在年齡較大時才[[分娩|分娩]]的婦女，不過有關年齡的定義，有許多不同的標準<ref name=Fretts2012>[http://www.uptodate.com/contents/effect-of-advanced-age-on-fertility-and-pregnancy-in-women Effect of advanced age on fertility and pregnancy in women] {{Wayback|url=http://www.uptodate.com/contents/effect-of-advanced-age-on-fertility-and-pregnancy-in-women |date=20160619172839 }} at [[UpToDate|UpToDate]]. Author: Ruth C Fretts. Section Editor: Louise Wilkins-Haug. Deputy Editor: Vanessa A Barss. This topic last updated: Dec 3, 2012.</ref>。<!--The variability in definitions  is in part explained by the effects of increasing age occurring as a {{link-en||Continuum (measurement)|continuum}} rather than as a threshold effect.<ref name="Fretts2012" />-->

在西歐、北歐及南歐，初次懷孕的婦女其平均年齡是27至29歲，在1970年代初期則是23至25歲。在一些歐洲國家（例如西班牙），初次懷孕的婦女平均年齡已經超過30歲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oecd.org/els/soc/SF2.3%20Mean%20age%20of%20mother%20at%20first%20childbirth%20-%20updated%20240212.pdf |title=SF2.3: Mean age of mothers at first childbirth |accessdate=2014-05-27 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141222133841/http://www.oecd.org/els/soc/SF2.3%20Mean%20age%20of%20mother%20at%20first%20childbirth%20-%20updated%20240212.pdf |archivedate=2014-12-22 }}</ref>。

初次懷孕年齡後延的現象不只在歐洲出現，[[亚洲|亚洲]]、[[日本|日本]]及美國也有類似情形，而且在[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]、[[土耳其|土耳其]]及[[伊朗|伊朗]]等新興國家也有類似情形。美國2016年初次懷孕年齡的平均年齡是在26.6歲<ref name="cdc.gov">{{Cite web |url=https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/fastats/births.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2019-11-14 |archive-date=2019-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191112144911/https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/fastats/births.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

高齡產婦和懷孕的不良副作用有關，例如增加[[女性不孕症|女性不孕症]]的風險<ref name=Leridon2004>[http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/oup/humrep/2004/00000019/00000007/art01548] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/oup/humrep/2004/00000019/00000007/art01548 |date=20121025132947 }} [http://humrep.oxfordjournals.org/content/19/7/1548] {{Wayback|url=http://humrep.oxfordjournals.org/content/19/7/1548 |date=20160706105528 }}
{{Cite journal | last1 = Leridon | first1 = H. | title = Can assisted reproduction technology compensate for the natural decline in fertility with age? A model assessment | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_human-reproduction_2004-07_19_7/page/1548 | doi = 10.1093/humrep/deh304 | journal = Human Reproduction | volume = 19 | issue = 7 | pages = 1548–1553 | year = 2004 | pmid =  15205397| pmc = }}</ref>，孩童出現[[染色体畸变|染色体畸变]]的風險也會提高<ref name=morris>{{cite journal|last=Morris|first=JK|author2=Mutton, DE|author3= Alberman, E|title=Revised estimates of the maternal age specific live birth prevalence of Down's syndrome.|journal=Journal of Medical Screening|date=2002|volume=9|issue=1|pages=2–6|pmid=11943789|doi=10.1136/jms.9.1.2}}</ref>，對應的{{link-en|父親年齡效應|paternal age effect}}比較少被提到<ref name="Tournaye-2009">H. Tournaye, "[https://books.google.com/books?id=-SlaAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA104 Male Reproductive Ageing] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-SlaAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA104 |date=20200517172924 }}," in Bewley, Ledger, and Nikolaou, eds., ''Reproductive Ageing'', Cambridge University Press (2009), {{ISBN|9781906985134}} (accessed 15 November 2013)</ref><ref name="Kidd-2001">{{cite journal |vauthors=Kidd SA, Eskenazi B, Wyrobek AJ |title=Effects of male age on semen quality and fertility: a review of the literature |journal=Fertil Steril |volume=75 |issue=2 |pages=237–48 |year=2001 |pmid=11172821 |doi= 10.1016/S0015-0282(00)01679-4|url= }}</ref>。

現今的世代較常有在年齡較長時才生育的情形。許多因素會影響夫妻決定生第一個小孩的時機，這些因素也包括教育、社會及經濟情形。 
==妊娠風險==
年紀越大，患上[[妊娠高血壓|妊娠高血壓]]或[[妊娠糖尿病|妊娠糖尿病]]機會將會比年輕產婦高，出現內科併發症如[[心臟病|心臟病]]或[[腎臟病|腎臟病]]、[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]的機會也會比較高。由於卵子老化，[[染色體異常|染色體異常]]的機會也會比年輕產婦高，增加胎兒發育不正常的機會，例如[[唐氏綜合症|唐氏綜合症]]。另外，高齡產婦也比較容易產生自發性[[流產|流產]]、[[早產|早產]]、[[胎盤早期剝離|胎盤早期剝離]]等情況。

